<!-- From the Blog Section -->
<section id="blog-section" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-gray-900/20 border-y border-gray-800/60">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4 animate-on-scroll">
        From the Blog
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 animate-on-scroll" style="--delay: 0.1s">
        Financial insights, app updates, and guides to help you master your money.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div id="recent-posts-container" class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      {% set posts = collections.post | reverse %}
      {% for post in posts.slice(0, 3) %}
      <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="blog-card animate-on-scroll" style="--delay: {{ loop.index0 * 0.1 }}s">
        <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}" class="blog-card-image" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='https://placehold.co/600x400/18181b/3f3f46?text=Image+Not+Found';">
        <div class="p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow">
          <span class="blog-card-date">{{ post.date | dateFilter }}</span>
          <h3 class="blog-card-title">{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
          <p class="blog-card-excerpt mt-auto">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
        </div>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <div class="text-center mt-12 animate-on-scroll" style="--delay: 0.3s">
      <a href="/blog/" class="cta-button-secondary">
        View All Posts <i class="fas fa-arrow-right ml-2"></i>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Project Story Section -->
<section id="story" class="py-24 md:py-32">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl text-center">
    <img
      src="img/AanjeloNoText.svg"
      alt="Aanjelo Salgado Logo"
      class="h-12 mx-auto mb-6 animate-on-scroll"
      onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='https://placehold.co/100x48/121212/e67e26?text=AS&font=satoshi';"
    />
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6 animate-on-scroll" style="--delay: 0.1s">
      From a Personal Need to a Public Tool
    </h2>
    <div class="text-lg text-gray-400 space-y-4 animate-on-scroll" style="--delay: 0.2s">
      <p>
        I needed a tool that matched how I think about money. Not dumbed down, not full of ads, not locked to a cloud server I don't control.
      </p>
      <p>
        After three years of managing money in Google Sheets and 20 days to build the first working version, Kaasi was born. It's been growing ever since. I built it for myself, but I hope it helps you manage your
        <span class="text-orange-500 font-semibold">කාසි</span>
        better, too.
